        Parameters:
        lowerRollerExtension - The talon that extends the lower roller.
        upperRoller - The spark controlling the upper roller.
        lowerRoller - The spark controlling the lower roller.
        flowerOpen - The solenoid that opens and closes the hatch mechanism.
        flowerForward - The solenoid that extends and retracts the hatch mechanism.
        cargoDetector - The cargo detection sensor.
        hatchDistanceSensor - The hatch detection sensor (taken off real robot).

        public void initDefaultCommand()
        Description copied from class: edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.command.Subsystem
        Initialize the default command for a subsystem By default subsystems have no default command, but if they do, the default command is set with this method. It is called on all Subsystems by CommandBase in the users program after all the Subsystems are created.
